            <span class="text-green-500 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong>REST API</strong> &mdash; JSON API for sending transactional emails via <code>POST /:domain/messages</code></span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-500 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong>Async processing</strong> &mdash; BullMQ job queue with retry and exponential backoff</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-500 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong>SMTP relay</strong> &mdash; Built-in Postfix MTA for outbound delivery</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-500 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong>Multiple recipients</strong> &mdash; Single address or array of addresses per message</span>
